    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"939943\">Xuanmizhen</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/Support.20.CF.84.20.28tau.29.20as.20the.20circle.20constant.20in.20fork.20of.20Mathlib.3F/near/537109392\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Is it possible to define <code>tau</code> as the period of <code>sin</code> or <code>cos</code>?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Certainly!</p>",
