        "sender_full_name": "Johan Commelin",
        "timestamp": 1756733691
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>OK. Then I think maybe I can prove these lemmas with <code>λ</code>, which is <code>τ / 4</code>. I'll define <code>λ</code> first, prove the period, and define <code>τ</code>.</p>",
